  time complexity
single key map to diff data structure like string(one single value),list(multiple value in one key),
set(many unique values under one key), hash(multiple key value pairs in one key like json)

vertical = kitna object ka size, key value pairs
number of keys and size of keys depends upon RAM(agr 8 gb hai to millions of keys store kr skte )


